---
import TextJustify from "../../components/TextJustify.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="KnobDroid and ShelfDroid Privacy Policy">
<div class="xl:max-w-2xl mx-auto p-2 xl:py-2">
  <Header mt={false}>Privacy Policy</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    This Privacy Policy applies to KnobDroid and ShelfDroid, two open source Android apps published
    by Halim.
  </TextJustify>
  <TextJustify>
    Both apps are designed to work without collecting, storing, or sharing your personal data.
  </TextJustify>
  <TextJustify>
    If you use KnobDroid or ShelfDroid, no account registration is required and no user data is
    transmitted to us.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Data Collection</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    KnobDroid and ShelfDroid do not collect personal information, usage analytics, crash reports,
    log data, advertising identifiers, contact information, location data, or any other user data.
  </TextJustify>
  <TextJustify>
    We do not ask you to create an account, sign in, or submit personal details in order to use
    these apps.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Data Storage</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    Any data created while you use the apps stays on your device unless you choose to export,
    back up, or share it yourself. We do not operate servers for collecting app data, log data, or
    diagnostics from users.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Third-Party Services</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    KnobDroid and ShelfDroid do not use third-party analytics, advertising SDKs, or remote tracking
    services to collect user information.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Open Source</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    Because these apps are open source, you can review the source code to verify how they handle
    data and what permissions they use.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Children’s Privacy</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    Since KnobDroid and ShelfDroid do not collect personal data, they do not knowingly collect data
    from children or adults.
  </TextJustify>

  <Header>Changes to This Privacy Policy</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time if the apps change. Any updates will be
    posted on this page.
  </TextJustify>

  <TextJustify>This policy is effective as of 2026-05-03</TextJustify>

  <Header>Contact Us</Header>
  <TextJustify>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact
    <a class="text-accent" href="mailto: dev@halim.dev">dev@halim.dev</a>.
  </TextJustify>
</div>
</Layout>
